%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%E1%BB%9F-c%C3%B4ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-gi%C3%A1c-%C6%B0ng-ca/poem-ME2CJyvEGcZc23MRGT-dHQ">Khương Sở công hoạ giác ưng ca - 姜楚公畫角鷹歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Huy-Li%E1%BB%85n/Nam-l%E1%BB%99-ch%C3%AD-S%C6%A1n-Thu%E1%BB%B7-t%E1%BB%B1-ng%E1%BB%99-Dao-C%C3%B9-V%C5%A9-H%E1%BB%AFu-L%E1%BB%A3i-c%C3%B4ng/poem-fNHkxXTwgzwd5pAxd6jthA">Nam lộ chí Sơn Thuỷ tự ngộ Dao Cù Vũ Hữu Lợi công - 南路至山水寺遇瑤衢武有利公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Huy-Li%E1%BB%85n/author-aojK5yt7X8rTWmkDYWXgEg">Trần Huy Liễn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nghi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/Qu%C3%A2n-th%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BA%A3o-thu/poem-I56S17mvTA07P0mMVGNxtg">Quân thành tảo thu - 軍城早秋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nghi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/author-LkgRymP1ghPPuP-xPE0EkA">Nghiêm Vũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%BF/T%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-OOnA9B1HOoPXjqaQhd0x7g">Tòng quân từ kỳ 1 - 從軍詞其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%BF/author-XqKtUVvcrpGk9S-tbvHI0Q">Hàn Thượng Quế</a>)<br></div>	</div>
